  "notes": "HAR-434 adds executable local-runtime parity for a partially received shipment that still carries unreceived incoming inventory. The scenario proves receive, quantity update, delete, and downstream inventory reads stay consistent without runtime Shopify writes; direct live shipment recording remains blocked by missing read/write inventory shipment scopes documented in the HAR-306 fixture."
